{
  "stem": "26142.9",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's very, very dangerous, absolutely impossible, to cross the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here we are in October, and this is the Carpathian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's not unusual in the Carpathian that in October, sometimes you get snow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In November, definitely you can get snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you have snow, you have to cross a mountain in the snow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what do we do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Finally, we stay there-- I don't remember-- eight or 10 days in Dolina.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we decided, my brother and I, Tsvi and I decided, since we are alone-- Moshe with the children cannot go with us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We should go alone, try to cross that border, and maybe we can get in touch with our-- we knew that our parents are still in Torun.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we also knew that they had money because they gave us money when we parted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we decided that we will take the chance, and when we will get over there, maybe we will be able to send somebody across for money and bring him back because we knew that the rabbi of Munkacs, the community, the Jewish community in Munkacs, managed to send somebody in to bring them over.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we knew that maybe for money this could be done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So one day we decided we are going next morning, and whatever we had money, we left our money-- Hungarian money-- we left it to my brother, Moshe but we left ourselves 40 pengos.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We need-- at least we surely had a few dollars in our pocket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the meantime, somehow or other, two brothers by the name of the Prisent found out about us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were also from Torun.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
